":guilabel:`Aflettercode Employment Hero-btw` in."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/employment_hero.rst:54
msgid "How does the API work?"
msgstr "Hoe werkt de API?"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/employment_hero.rst:None
