msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrijwillige bijdrage-optie`: kies :guilabel:`Alleen verplichte "
"bijdrage`, :guilabel:`Met vast %VC` of :guilabel:`Max 5% VC`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:51
